snippet.title: Aztec - The Curse in the Heart of the City of Gold (intro)
snippet.description:
European Playstation game from 2001.  This will be my next walkthrough project, as soon as I my brain recovers from completing Rhem 4.  There is an audio problem with the dialog at the end of this video which will be fixed for the walkthrough.   

Game suggestion by mircoseli.  Thank you!
